      Of course, the law should be tightened up.  But this is still a pound of cure, when an ounce of prevention will do.<br/><br/>I'm a federal whistleblower who tried the legal route, so I know its *limitations* for relief  even if we add the "ideal" legal language.<br/><br/>Time to start replacing the need to go to court with technology that prevents retaliation in the first place.  See my Idea:<br/><br/>"Make It Safe for Govt. Workers to Innovate to Save Money"<br/><br/>http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/dtd/2481-4049<br/><br/>

                  
